<br>1. To provide you with products or services requested by you; 
<br>2. Where you have consented to the use or disclosure; 
<br>3. Where we have notified you of the intended use or disclosure; 
<br>4. For the purposes for which we collected it, and for related purposes which you would reasonably expect, which may include: 
