<br><br></span></p><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-9262e1ae"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-3c899262">THIRD-PARTY SERVICES</span></h4><p class="sc-oUAoT HrWqm pf-9332e639" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-39579332">In general, the third-party providers used by us will only collect, use and disclose your information to the extent necessary to allow them to perform the services they provide to us.
<br>
<br>However, certain third-party service providers, such as payment gateways and other payment transaction processors, have their own privacy policies in respect to the information we are required to provide to them for your purchase-related transactions.
